  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the exercise protocol called &quot;Siriraj home base
      exercise program for OA knee&quot; to usual care and physical modalities for conservative
      treatment in patients with 1st OA knee.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
